MoodMusic Workflow

This project is a hybrid music recommendation system that suggests songs based on user mood and preferences.

Dataset
Used a Spotify tracks dataset with audio features like valence, energy, danceability, and acousticness.
Created a synthetic ratings dataset to simulate user-song interactions for collaborative filtering.
Data Preparation
Cleaned and processed the dataset using generate_songs_dataset.py
Generated user ratings using generate_synthetic_ratings.py
Recommendation Approach
Content-Based Filtering: Recommends songs based on similarity of audio features.
Collaborative Filtering: Uses matrix factorization to learn user preferences from ratings.
Hybrid Model: Combines both approaches for better recommendations.
Files
generate_songs_dataset.py – prepares song dataset
generate_synthetic_ratings.py – creates ratings data
main.py – runs the recommendation system
